headline: Phillip Allen Sharp Improved Human Health With Breakthroughs
summary: Phillip Allen Sharp grew up on a small tobacco farm in rural Falmouth, Ky. That may seem an unlikely place to launch a science career.

headline: Biogen's Autoimmune Disease Candidate Gets FDA's Breakthrough Status
summary: BIIB secures FDA's Breakthrough Therapy status for litifilimab in cutaneous lupus, backed by phase II results, while advancing phase III and broader lupus studies.
